author: philip
msg: First cut at providing 'svn diff -rREV1:REV2' repository to repository
diffs. Lots of things work, but some remaining problems are: directory
deletes are not yet shown, file deletes are not shown using ra_dav,
using an URL to items not in HEAD doesn't work.
(svn_client_diff): Change prototype to pass two revisions.
(wc_repository_diff): Allow two revisions and pass them to svn_client_diff.
(svn_client_diff): Now takes two revisions and either a working copy path
or an URL. Compares wc-to-repos or repos-to-repos as appropriate.
New file that implements svn_client__get_diff_editor to do repos-to-repos
